  "page": {
    "documentTitle": "雙曲貼現 | Concept Reading Lab",
    "bodyClass": "knowledge-page knowledge-hyperbolic-discounting",
    "heroHtml": "<div class=\"hero-inner\">\n  <div>\n    <p class=\"kicker\">Knowledge Study / time / temptation / tradeoff</p>\n    <h1>雙曲貼現</h1>\n    <p class=\"topic-subtitle\">Hyperbolic Discounting</p>\n    <p class=\"thesis\">越靠近眼前的得失，心理重量常越不成比例地放大，讓人明知道長期更好，仍反覆把決策讓給現在這一刻。</p>\n    <div class=\"hero-prompt\">\n      <strong>Read For</strong>\n      <p>這一頁要把『我不重視長期』和『只是眼前太有吸力』拆開，因為很多拖延與短視決策都和時間貼現形狀有關。</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <aside class=\"hero-note\" aria-label=\"主題資訊\">\n    <dl class=\"lexical-meta lexical-meta--knowledge\" aria-label=\"主題摘要\">\n      <div>\n        <dt>主題類型</dt>\n        <dd>時間偏誤 / 立即誘惑</dd>\n      </div>\n      <div>\n        <dt>核心問題</dt>\n        <dd>We overvalue immediate rewards relative to future ones</dd>\n      </div>\n      <div>\n        <dt>主要判準</dt>\n        <dd>即時獎勵、延遲回報、自制成本、承諾裝置</dd>\n      </div>\n      <div>\n        <dt>讀完產出</dt>\n        <dd>能看出哪些決策不是價值觀變了，而是現在這一刻把未來壓太扁了</dd>\n      </div>\n    </dl>\n    <div class=\"knowledge-map\" aria-label=\"閱讀結構示意\">\n      <span>現在</span>\n      <span>未來</span>\n      <span>偏重</span>\n    </div>\n  </aside>\n</div>",
    "mainHtml": "<aside class=\"compass\" aria-label=\"頁內導覽\">\n  <span>Reading Path</span>\n  <a href=\"#core\">讀法總覽</a>\n  <a href=\"#setup\">問題設定</a>\n  <a href=\"#lenses\">判準透鏡</a>\n  <a href=\"#psychology\">心理連結</a>\n  <a href=\"#applications\">現實映射</a>\n  <a href=\"#misreadings\">誤讀校正</a>\n  <a href=\"#questions\">延伸提問</a>\n  <a href=\"#sources\">來源</a>\n</aside>\n\n<article class=\"article\">\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"core\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Orientation</p>\n      <h2>不是未來沒價值，而是現在太會搶鏡頭</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">雙曲貼現抓到的是時間上的不穩定：遠看很理性，臨到眼前又常改口。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"core-card\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Core Tension</p>\n      <p>長期規劃能看見累積效益，但當短期誘惑或不適真正靠近時，原本的理性排序很容易被重新洗牌。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"principle-strip\" aria-label=\"本頁讀法\">\n      <div>\n        <span>01</span>\n        <strong>先看誘惑何時最強</strong>\n        <p>問題常不是整體不理性，而是臨近決策時偏好突然變形。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div>\n        <span>02</span>\n        <strong>再設計承諾裝置</strong>\n        <p>若知道未來的自己會軟，最好現在就替他設護欄。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div>\n        <span>03</span>\n        <strong>最後降低延遲痛感</strong>\n        <p>把長期好處拆成更近、可見的小回饋，能減少被眼前拖走。</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"setup\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Setup</p>\n      <h2>從一個遠看很清楚、近看卻總是做不到的決定開始</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">雙曲貼現在儲蓄、健康、學習與任何需要延遲滿足的工作裡都常見。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"definition-grid\">\n      <div class=\"tile\">\n        <strong>最小劇情</strong>\n        <p>你週日決定這週每天留一小時補文件，但到每天晚上，眼前的疲勞與其他即時回報總是把那一小時吃掉。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"tile\">\n        <strong>真正難點</strong>\n        <p>未來的好處不是不存在，而是在接近當下時常輸給現在的小痛或小爽。</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"concept-flow\" aria-label=\"問題展開\">\n      <div class=\"flow-step\">遠期目標看起來值得</div>\n      <div class=\"flow-arrow\">→</div>\n      <div class=\"flow-step\">短期誘惑靠近</div>\n      <div class=\"flow-arrow\">→</div>\n      <div class=\"flow-step\">偏好往即時回報傾斜</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"paradox-frame\">\n      <strong>Key Point</strong>\n      <p>雙曲貼現提醒你：很多反覆失守不是因為不知道什麼對，而是因為『現在』的權重太大。</p>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"lenses\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Lenses</p>\n      <h2>四個看時間拉力的角度</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">如果某件事總是遠看能答應、近看做不到，通常值得懷疑時間貼現形狀。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"lens-grid\">\n      <article class=\"lens-card\">\n        <strong>即時誘惑</strong>\n        <p>現在能立刻得到什麼，或立刻少承受什麼？</p>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"lens-card\">\n        <strong>延遲收益</strong>\n        <p>長期好處有多抽象、多遠、多不被感受到？</p>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"lens-card\">\n        <strong>承諾裝置</strong>\n        <p>你是否有機制幫未來的自己守住今天答應的事？</p>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"lens-card\">\n        <strong>環境設計</strong>\n        <p>是否能讓正確選項在當下也比較容易被做到？</p>\n      </article>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"table-wrap\">\n      <table>\n        <thead>\n          <tr>\n            <th>情境</th>\n            <th>遠看想做什麼</th>\n            <th>近看常發生什麼</th>\n          </tr>\n        </thead>\n        <tbody>\n          <tr>\n            <td>健康習慣</td>\n            <td>想持續運動</td>\n            <td>眼前疲勞讓人選擇休息</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>技術債整理</td>\n            <td>知道該補文件與測試</td>\n            <td>短期 feature 壓力總先贏</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>財務規劃</td>\n            <td>想存下更多</td>\n            <td>即時消費的快感更有拉力</td>\n          </tr>\n        </tbody>\n      </table>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"psychology\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Psychology</p>\n      <h2>為什麼越靠近眼前，偏好越容易歪</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">因為大腦對立即回饋和立即不適本來就更敏感，未來值則容易被抽象化。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"example-grid\">\n      <div class=\"example\">\n        <strong>現在更有感</strong>\n        <p>立刻的爽與痛會比未來的抽象結果更強烈。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"example\">\n        <strong>未來自己像陌生人</strong>\n        <p>我們常替未來版本的自己做出自己未必會守的承諾。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"example\">\n        <strong>小失守會連續發生</strong>\n        <p>每次都只偏一點，長期卻會累積成巨大差距。</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"micro-note\">雙曲貼現不是道德失敗，而是時間權重本來就不均勻的心理事實。</p>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"applications\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Applications</p>\n      <h2>把承諾裝置帶回學習、流程與產品設計</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">對個人習慣、團隊節奏與產品設計來說，理解雙曲貼現能幫你少把短視完全怪給意志力。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"example-grid\">\n      <div class=\"example\">\n        <strong>文件與測試</strong>\n        <p>重要但延遲回報的工作最容易一再被眼前 feature 吃掉。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"example\">\n        <strong>儲蓄與備援</strong>\n        <p>平時看都知道要做，只有當下要多花一點成本時最容易延後。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"example\">\n        <strong>產品體驗</strong>\n        <p>若產品想鼓勵長期好行為，必須想辦法在當下也給出可感回饋。</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <ul class=\"bullet-list\">\n      <li>與其只要求自律，不如先設計讓正確行為在當下也較容易發生的環境。</li>\n      <li>凡是總被『今天先算了』吃掉的事，都值得用承諾裝置重新包裝一次。</li>\n    </ul>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"misreadings\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Misreadings</p>\n      <h2>三個常見誤讀</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">雙曲貼現不是說人不在乎未來，而是說未來的票面重量會隨時間形變。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"collocation-list\" aria-label=\"常見誤讀\">\n      <article class=\"collocation-card\">\n        <div>\n          <strong>只要自制力強就沒事</strong>\n          <span class=\"register-tag\">校正</span>\n        </div>\n        <p>自制力重要，但環境與承諾裝置同樣關鍵。</p>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"collocation-card\">\n        <div>\n          <strong>這只發生在小習慣</strong>\n          <span class=\"register-tag\">校正</span>\n        </div>\n        <p>專案排程、投資與風險管理也都深受影響。</p>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"collocation-card\">\n        <div>\n          <strong>知道長期比較好就會做到</strong>\n          <span class=\"register-tag\">校正</span>\n        </div>\n        <p>認知知道與當下做到之間常隔著很大的時間偏重。</p>\n      </article>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"questions\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Questions</p>\n      <h2>我現在放棄長期價值，是因為真的不值得，還是因為今天太近</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">下面兩個問題很適合放在反覆拖延的事項前。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"prompt-grid\">\n      <article class=\"prompt-card\">\n        <strong>如果這個決定提前一週做，我還會選同樣答案嗎</strong>\n        <p>差異很大時，時間貼現通常已在主導。</p>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"prompt-card\">\n        <strong>我能不能先替未來的自己設一個比較不會臨陣變卦的護欄</strong>\n        <p>這是抵抗雙曲貼現最實用的路。</p>\n      </article>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"template-note\">\n      <strong>延伸路線</strong>\n      <p>延伸閱讀可接 present bias、commitment device 與 self-control。</p>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"sources\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Sources</p>\n      <h2>來源與整理方式</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">這一頁以 hyperbolic discounting 為主，再把概念帶回習慣、專案與延遲回報設計。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"source-grid\">\n      <article class=\"source-card\">\n        <strong>主概念</strong>\n        <p>Hyperbolic discounting 條目整理了人如何對較近的回報給出不成比例高的權重。</p>\n        <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hyperbolic_discounting\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Hyperbolic Discounting</a>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"source-card\">\n        <strong>相鄰偏誤</strong>\n        <p>Present bias 可作為對照，理解當下偏好的行為版本。</p>\n        <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Present_bias\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Present Bias</a>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"source-card\">\n        <strong>對策概念</strong>\n        <p>Commitment device 條目有助於把這個偏誤轉成可操作的護欄設計。</p>\n        <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Commitment_device\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Commitment Device</a>\n      </article>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\">\n    <div class=\"reference-box\">\n      <div>\n        <p class=\"section-label\">Reference</p>\n        <h2>下一步</h2>\n        <p>讀完後可以挑一件你總在『明天開始』的事，先想一個今天就能設下的承諾裝置。</p>\n      </div>\n      <a class=\"reference-link\" href=\"../knowledge-topic-template.html\">打開模板</a>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</article>"
  }
}
